Paper: hep-th/9809004

Date: 1998-09-01

Title: Gauge Consistent Wilson Renormalization Group I

Authors: Michele Simionato

Comments: Latex2e, 39 pages, 3 eps figures. Revised version to appear in Int.

J. Mod. PhysJournal-ref: Int.J.Mod.Phys. A15 (2000) 2121-2152

A version of the Wilson Renormalization Group Equation consistent with gaugesymmetry is presented. A perturbative renormalizability proof is established. Awilsonian derivation of the Callan-Symanzik equation is given.